      SYS: OPERATIONAL &nbsp;::&nbsp; OAUTH: /auth/google &nbsp;::&nbsp; TLS 1.3 ACTIVE &nbsp;::&nbsp; TOKENS: JWT-SIGNED &nbsp;::&nbsp; FIREWALL: ENABLED &nbsp;::&nbsp; INTRUSION DETECTION: ON &nbsp;::&nbsp; ALL NODES NOMINAL &nbsp;::&nbsp; UPLINK: STABLE &nbsp;::&nbsp;
